{
  "stem": "21319.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You want the name?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One is in Russian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one is in Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One was [RUSSIAN].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But-- and the other one was [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's a dance with a doll.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Russian was a different solo dance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's the only thing I remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, myself, didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because my friends were Christian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Only in 1939-- 1938 and '39, I had a few close Christian friends.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and they-- it-- it became a big propaganda to kill the Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I remember, I was walking down the streets.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a kid, a little boy of eight or nine years old, come over to me and start saying oh, you Jew, you Jew.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, and using foul language.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I run away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because if I would hit him, I would be arrested.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The last two years, when Jozef Pilsudski, the famous-- he was the general and he was also the President for a while in Poland-- was a Jewish friend form the First World War.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the last couple of years, the influence of Nazis were very big in Poland, especially in Vilna, where I was.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they spread it to the young people to every-- if somebody didn't have a job, it's the Jews' fault.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anything they could.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the anti-Semitism the last couple of years were very bad in mine town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the few friends what I had, the Polish friends, they stayed away form me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They said that there's a problem.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They can't come to visit me because they will be-- they will be pointed out, that they have Jewish friends.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was a very bad situation, the last couple of years before the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
